{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01U4jdwRbC99aA62EAP8HgPY","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The mongodb namespace exists but is empty. I need to deploy a 3-node MongoDB replica set with:\n1. A headless Service named `mongodb-replica-svc`\n2. A StatefulSet named `mongodb-replica` with 3 replicas\n3. Admin user: admin-user / admin123password (stored in Secret `admin-user-password`)\n4. App user: app-user / app123password (stored in Secret `app-user-password`)\n5. Keyfile for internal authentication\n6. Replica set named `mongodb-replica`\n\nLet me plan the deployment:\nI'll start by creating the necessary secrets for the keyfile and user passwords, then set up the headless Service for cluster communication, and finally deploy the StatefulSet with MongoDB 6.0 configured for replica set mode with authentication enabled.\n\nFor the StatefulSet, I'll mount the keyfile from the secret and pass the replica set and keyfile options to mongod. After the pods are running, I'll need to initialize the replica set and create the admin and app users by executing commands in the primary pod—I can do this either through a post-start hook or by manually running initialization commands once the cluster is ready.\n\nThe key insight is that MongoDB's localhost exception allows me to connect without credentials on a fresh install, even with auth enabled. So I'll deploy with auth and keyfile authentication already configured, then use that localhost exception to initialize the replica set and create the first admin user.\n\nNow I'm setting up the StatefulSet configuration with the MongoDB container running with both `--auth` and `--keyFile` flags pointing to the keyfile mounted in the pod.\n\nI need to generate the keyfile using openssl and then handle the initialization timing carefully, since I'll need to wait for the replica set to elect a primary before running the setup commands.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":131,"cache_read_input_tokens":29806,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":131},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3c5e6ff9-a9d2-41d5-a983-3b2d4d7afa4e","uuid":"c96bb495-fbee-47fb-bffb-adeffb370df5","request_id":"req_011Cc59aTcDt13QCPqctyeAg"}
